latestPosts.caption:
GRWM AFTER 2 LONG YEARS!! PLEASE SHOW SOME LOVE & DROP A ♥️ if you missed me on your feed 💫 I cannot express it into words about how badly I wanted to get back to filming & posting content after having Kai 👶 there were so many times I thought that I should get up and just film but there’s just been TOO MUCH on my plate , postpartum Depression , MAJOR body image issues, tons of hair fall and what not!  So after I had kai - obviously I got busy taking care of him , then started my brand , joined hubby’s firm as the lead designer. BUT as much as I was grateful about having all of these moments in my life , I somewhere lost myself and mourned to find my self again. I’m so glad I had you as my support system every step of the way and you’ve always pushed me to do better , be better and just grow @sahil_narang12 - so an equal credit goes to you too ! So here’s me , after a long breakkkkk but STILL HERE!

Two years ago, you came into our lives and brought with you so much love, joy, and light. Watching you grow has been the most incredible journey, and I’m so proud of the little person you’re becoming.
 I hope this year brings you endless happiness, exciting discoveries, and all the cuddles and giggles you can handle.
